You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart rope skipping. After connecting Alexa to your FuHai Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "FuHai Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our "FuHai Home" app;
(3). You need to have some devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "FuHai Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Smart rope skipping" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smart rope skipping" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smart rope skipping", and you'll be navigated to "Smart rope skipping" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa，turn on smart rope skipping
Alexa，turn off smart rope skipping
Alexa，start smart rope skipping
Alexa，pause smart rope skipping
